This plugin sorta works, so I'll release it. Thanks for the nudge.

Instructions are complicated. Videos are simple. Go here:
   http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RlWtJPj0PXk
   http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dRxLMMNG8II

Note that this plugin for wordpress is completely unstyled, and the results-display page template is not autogenerated.

COMPETITION
    I envision this plugin being good for publications or sports news, which need the ability to customize and drive content and advertising. For others, you might consider...
  - Challonge.com  (if you just want something simple and flashy)
  - other? Let me know!